<script>
  document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
    var endlessScroll = new Ajaxinate({

      container: '#Huratips-Loop',
      pagination: '#Huratips-Pagination',
      loadingText: '<center><img src="//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0488/9201/8848/t/98/assets/Comp-1.gif?v=7944825952630072034"></center>',
      callback: function() {
        convertPricesToUSD();
      }
    });
  });
</script>

<script type="text/javascript">
  const collFilters = document.querySelectorAll('.filter-checkbox');
  const sortBy = document.getElementById("SortBy");
  const swatches = document.querySelectorAll('.product-quickshop input');
  const collFiltersRefine = document.querySelectorAll('.refine-checkbox');
  
  function applyFilterSortby() {
    var newTags = [];
    collFilters.forEach((collFilter) => {
      if(collFilter.checked && collFilter.value != "") {
        newTags.push(collFilter.value);
      }
    });
    var sort = sortBy.value;
  
    if (newTags.length) {
      var query = newTags.join('+');
      window.location.href = '/collections/sale-unstitched/' + query + '?sort_by=' + sort;
    }
    else {
      
        window.location.href = '/collections/sale-unstitched' + '?sort_by=' + sort;
      
    }
  }
      
  function refineFilterinit(getClick) {
      debugger;
      console.log("Refine JJ");   
      var currentTags = [];
      collFiltersRefine.forEach((collFilterRefine) => {
          if( collFilterRefine.checked && collFilterRefine.value != "" )
          {
              currentTags.push(collFilterRefine.value);
          }
      });
      console.log(currentTags);
      console.log(getClick);

      if (getClick)
      {
          var sort = sortBy.value;

          if (currentTags.length) {
              var query = currentTags.join('+');
              window.location.href = '/collections/sale-unstitched/' + query + '?sort_by=' + sort;
          }
          else {
              
              window.location.href = '/collections/sale-unstitched' + '?sort_by=' + sort;
              
          }
      }  
  }
  
  if (collFilters.length > 0) {
    collFilters.forEach((collFilter) => {
      collFilter.addEventListener('change', function(){
        applyFilterSortby();
      });
    });
  }
   
   if ( collFiltersRefine.length > 0 ) {
    
      var refineClick = false;
      collFiltersRefine.forEach((collFilterRefine) => {
          collFilterRefine.addEventListener('change', function(){
              refineClick = true;
              refineFilterinit(refineClick);  
          });
      });
      refineFilterinit(refineClick);
  }
  
  // Quickshop functionality
  $(document).ready(function() {
    $('body').on('change', '.product-quickshop input', function() {
      var variantID = $(this).val();
      $(this).closest('.product-quickshop').find('.product-form__variants').val(variantID);
      $(this).closest('.product-quickshop').find('.product-form__cart-submit').prop('disabled', false);
    });
  
    $('.filters__toggle').on('click', function() {
      var backdrop = $('<div id="sidebar-backdrop"></div>');
      $('body').append(backdrop);
      $('.sidebar').addClass("open");
      backdrop.on('click', function() {
        $(this).remove();
        $('.sidebar').removeClass("open");
      });
    });
  
    $(".sidebar__close").on('click', function() {
      $("#sidebar-backdrop").remove();
      $('.sidebar').removeClass("open");
    });
  });
  </script>

<script type="text/javascript">
function setCookie(cname, cvalue, exdays) {
  var d = new Date();
  d.setTime(d.getTime() + (exdays*24*60*60*1000));
  var expires = "expires="+ d.toUTCString();
  document.cookie = cname + "=" + cvalue + ";" + expires + ";path=/";
}

function getCookie(cname) {
  var name = cname + "=";
  var decodedCookie = decodeURIComponent(document.cookie);
  var ca = decodedCookie.split(';');
  for(var i = 0; i <ca.length; i++) {
    var c = ca[i];
    while (c.charAt(0) == ' ') {
      c = c.substring(1);
    }
    if (c.indexOf(name) == 0) {
      return c.substring(name.length, c.length);
    }
  }
  return "";
}

function convertPricesToUSD() {
    var cookie = getCookie("currency");
    if(cookie === "USD") {
        $('.money').each(function(i, el) {
            if($(el).attr("data-currency") === "PKR") {
                var price = $(el).text();
                price = parseInt(price.replace("PKR ", "").replace(",", ""));
                usdPrice = price / 170;
                usdPrice = Math.round(usdPrice * 100) / 100;
                $(el).text("USD " + usdPrice);
                $(el).attr("data-currency", "USD");
            }
        });
    }
}

$(document).ready(function() {
    var cookie = getCookie("currency");
    if(cookie === "") {
        console.log("Sending request to api")
         $.ajax({
             url: "https://mis.alchemative.net/country_baseon_ip",
             type: "GET",
             success: function(data) {
                 console.log(data)
                 if(data.country_code === "PK") {
                     setCookie("currency", "PKR", 1);
                 } else {
                     setCookie("currency", "USD", 1);
                     convertPricesToUSD();
                     $("#internationalNotice").show();
                 }
             },
             error: function(error) {
                 console.log(error)
             }
         });
    } else {
        console.log("Not sending request to api")
         convertPricesToUSD();
    }

    $("#internationalNotice .close").on('click', function() {
        $("#internationalNotice").fadeOut();
    });
});
</script>

<style type="text/css">
#internationalNotice {
    z-index: 999999;
}
</style>

//     Announcement bar hide and Toolbar sticky on scroll
    $(document).ready(function(){
      $(window).scroll(function(){

        if($(window).scrollTop() > 200){
          // $('.announcement-bar').css({
          //   'opacity': 0,
          //   'height': 0
          // });
          $('.site-header, nav.small--hide').addClass('header-sticky');
        }
        else{
          // if($(window).width() < 768){
          //   $('.announcement-bar.mob-only').css({
          //   'opacity': 1,
          //   'height': 'auto'
          // });
          // }else{
          //   $('.announcement-bar.desktop-only').css({
          //   'opacity': 1,
          //   'height': 'auto'
          // });
          // }
          $('.site-header, nav.small--hide').removeClass('header-sticky');
        }
        if($(window).scrollTop() > 250){
          if($(window).width() < 768){
            $('.filters-toolbar__item-wrapper').addClass('sticky-toolbar');
          }
        }else{
            $('.filters-toolbar__item-wrapper').removeClass('sticky-toolbar');
        }
      });
    });

    
  </script>
